Class: blueprint for creating Object
Object:real world entity,instance of Class
Encapsulation: hiding the essential feature of a Class
Inheritance: reusing the features of super class by inheriting the class and its properties
Polymorphism:object is performing multiple functionalities based on the function calls and the behaviour of the object gets changed
